<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>Give heed, O Lord Jesus Christ our God, from thy holy dwelling-place, and from the throne of glory of thy kingdom, and come to sanctify us, O thou who sittest on high together with the Father, and art here invisibly present with us. And vouchsafe to give us by thy mighty hand thy most pure Body and thy precious Blood, and through us to all the people.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
